# Study Night

A digital study solution for the modern world, featuring flashcard creation and study sessions.

## Tech Stack
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- Parcel (bundler)
- Gulp (task runner)
- Mocha/Chai (unit testing)
- Cypress (E2E testing)
- ESLint/Prettier (linting and formatting)

## Project Structure
- `nd0011-c4-starter/starter/`: Contains the app source code (`index.html`, `src/`, `styles/`, `images/`, `test/`, `e2e/`).
- `nd0011-c4-starter/cypress/`: Contains Cypress configuration and support files.
- `dist/`: Output directory for the built app.
- `gulpfile.cjs`: Gulp tasks for building, serving, and testing.

